<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>{{title}}</title>
</head>
<body>
  <div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center; margin: 0; padding: 20px;">
    <h1>{{title}}</h1>
    <p>Hello,</p>
    <p>You recently requested to reset your password for your {{appName}} account. Click the button below to reset it.</p>

    <a href="{{url}}" style="background-color: #f44336; color: white; padding: 14px 20px; font-size: 16px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; display: inline-block; margin-top: 20px;">{{action}}</a>

    <p>If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email.</p>

    <p>If you're having trouble clicking the button, copy and paste the following link into your browser:</p>
    <p><a href="{{url}}" style="color: #1a73e8;">{{url}}</a></p>

    <p>Best regards,</p>
    <p>{{appName}} Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
